						<div class="postbody">Nice. It might be better to write $80 to $400A, to avoid any length counter/linear counter issues (better to avoid messing with it if you can). So something like this as the simplest-but-effective approach:
<br />
<br />lda #$FF
<br />sta $400A
<br />lda high
<br />sta $400B
<br />lda low
<br />sta $400A</div>

