						<div class="postbody">Would it be worth caching the two values to be written into A and Y, and then writing them back-to-back.  You'll still have a race condition, but it will be down to 3 clock cycles instead of however many you currently have (8?).
<br />
<br />ie..
<br />
<br />lda something, X
<br />tay
<br />lda other, X
<br />sta APU_a
<br />sty APU_b</div>

